query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_leaks,
  SUM(CASE WHEN screenshotUrls IS NOT NULL AND screenshotUrls != '[]' AND screenshotUrls != 'null' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as with_screenshots,
  SUM(CASE WHEN screenshotUrls IS NULL OR screenshotUrls = '[]' OR screenshotUrls = 'null' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as without_screenshots
FROM leaks;
